{
  "description": "A stunning night view of a city skyline with a bridge prominently featured in the foreground. The bridge is illuminated with bright white lights, creating a long, glowing path across the dark water. Behind the bridge, a cityscape rises with numerous illuminated buildings, creating a dense cluster of lights. Fireworks are exploding in the sky above the city, adding vibrant bursts of color \u2013 primarily red and gold \u2013 to the scene. The skyline includes a tall, slender tower that appears to be the focal point of the fireworks display. The overall impression is one of a vibrant, lively city celebrating a special occasion. There\u2019s also a second bridge in the background.",
